  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: a82df9c0be154a2fb7717067f12ea6d4, type: 3}
  m_Name: DemonData_Hoa
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: LSG::LSG.DemonData_Hoa
  demonName: Hoa
  canDateDemonMultipleTimes: 0
  introDialogue: '"There''s a tremendous grinding of earth and metal and stone. 
    What rises through the portal is a rusted jalopy on cinderblocks, rimmed with
    tall tufts of grass that aspire to being wheat.  The tall, cuddly goatess on
    top tightens her flannel shirt and breaths out vapors of *very* freshly distilled
    moonshine.


    ""Well look who we have here!  You new in the neighborhood? 
    I got some empty properties next door you could move into.""


    "'
  minimumPowerLevel: 10
  maximumPowerLevel: 25
  outcome: Between dodging distillery explosions and traversing the suburban jungle
    that is her lawn, you're feeling much more physically fit than any reputable
    black magician has a right to be.  About as exhausted, though.
  boon: 
  bane: One of your non-white pages is randomly removed and cannot be purchased again
    this game.
  boonBaneDialogue: 
  dateOutcome: '"Concerts aren''t your normal go-to, but after three acts singing
    about running from cops, murdering abusive husbands, and generally having a grand
    hell of a time, Hoa cuddles up to you before dragging you out dancing.


    Every
    part of her is warm and soft, and you''ve never had a more pleasant tipsiness
    than this very moment.


    In the morning she is gone, but she left you a half
    dissassembled project car and an unlabeled bottle to remember her by."'
